replies.body:
{{champion:63}} : I would change his passive: flat damage + AP scaling;
{{champion:3}} : He need better base mana regen because he's unplayable even with chalice;
{{champion:74}} : A little buff to his late game H-28Q Apex Turret (his ulted turret);
{{champion:90}} : Less cooldown on his Q and maybe W at level 5. He has super high mana costs and he can't just spam even with Athene's.
{{champion:98}} : He's playable, but his kit his lackluster. His only gap closing is his only CC.
{{champion:50}} : Just fix his last hit animation pls
{{champion:106}} : He's unplayable in this meta. He need changes to his kit's mechanics.

Other champions just need a rework and I didn't mention them. I just want to say that I'm an {{champion:6}} main and buffing his is a madness.
